and the united kingdom where it offers specialized financial services it offers banking services including retail and corporate banking and wealth management which consists of trust private banking and asset management in bermuda and cayman islands segments it offers both banking and wealth management in guernsey bahamas and switzerland segments it offers wealth management in the united kingdom segment it offers residential property lending the bank provides foreign exchange services in the normal course of business in all jurisdictions its wealth management platform has three lines of business trust private banking and asset managementlending activitiesthe bank offers a set of lending offerings including residential mortgage lending automobile lending credit cards consumer financing and overdraft facilities to its retail customers and commercial real estate lending commercial and industrial loans and overdraft facilities to its commercial and corporate customers these offerings are provided to its retail commercial and private banking clients in its jurisdictions including bermuda and the cayman islands it also offers residential mortgage lending through its private banking business in guernsey and to its high net worth and ultrahigh net worth clients in the united kingdom the residential mortgage portfolio comprises mortgages to clients seeking to establish or already have a financial services relationship it includes mortgages to individuals and corporate loans secured by way of first ranking charges over the residential property to which each specific loan relates generally on terms which allow for the repossession and sale of the property if the borrower fails to comply with the terms of the loan it provides loans in respect of automobile financing consumer financing credit cards and overdraft facilities to retail and private banking clients in the jurisdictions in which the bank operates commercial real estate loans are offered to real estate investors developers and builders domiciled primarily in bermuda and the united kingdom its commercial real estate loan portfolio is broken down into two categories commercial mortgage and construction the commercial and industrial loan portfolio includes loans and overdraft facilities advanced primarily to corporations and small and mediumsized entities which are generally not collateralized by real estate and where loan repayments are expected to flow from the operation of the underlying businesses as of december   the bank had  billion of net loansinvestment activitiesthe banks investment portfolio includes securities issued or guaranteed by the united states government or federal agencies it also includes corporate debt securities assetbacked securitiesstudent loans commercial mortgagebacked securities and residential mortgagebacked securities as of december   its total securities available for sale amounted to  billionsources of fundsthe banks deposits are generated principally by banking business line which offers retail and corporate checking savings and term deposits through its segments in bermuda the cayman islands and guernsey in addition wealth management through its private banking business line also provides deposit services to high net worth and ultrahigh net worth clients in those same geographic segments as of december   the bank had total deposits of  billionsubsidiary activitiesthe banks subsidiaries include butterfield asset management limited butterfield trust bermuda limited bermuda trust company limited bermuda securities bermuda limited butterfield bank cayman limited butterfield trust cayman limited butterfield trust bahamas limited butterfield holdings switzerland limited butterfield trust switzerland limited and butterfield mortgages limited butterfield asset management limited provides asset management services butterfield trust bermuda limited and bermuda trust company limited provide corporate trustee fiduciary and corporate administration services bermuda securities bermuda limited provides investment advisory and listing sponsor services butterfield bank cayman limited provides banking services butterfield trust cayman limited provides trustee fiduciary and corporate administration services butterfield trust bahamas limited provides trust and fiduciary services butterfield holdings switzerland limited provides investment services butterfield trust switzerland limited provides trust and fiduciary services butterfield mortgages limited provides residential property lending services » full overview of ntb company address bank of nt butterfield  son ltd  front streethamilton     hm  p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation e barclay simmons  michael collins  michael schrum  daniel frumkin  shaun morris  » more officers  directors bank of nt butterfield  son ltd news » more ntb news related topics stocksstock screenerfinancialsbanks the bank of nt butterfield  son limited private company information  bloomberg july    pm et banks company overview of the bank of nt butterfield  son limited snapshot people company overview the bank of nt butterfield  son limited a community bank provides various specialized financial services to individuals and small to mediumsized and privately owned businesses primarily in bermuda the company accepts retail and corporate checking savings term and noninterest bearing deposits as well as certificates of deposits its lending portfolio includes residential mortgage lending automobile financing consumer financing credit cards overdraft facilities commercial real estate lending and commercial and industrial loans in addition the company offers investment products and services and cash and liquidity management foreign exchange custody administration and se the bank of nt butterfield  son limited a community bank provides various specialized financial services to individuals and small to mediumsized and privately owned businesses primarily in bermuda the company